    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Chop the <strong>warmed sourdough pitta</strong> into quarters</p><p>Serve the <strong>hummus</strong> on a plate with the <strong>roasted veg mix</strong>,<strong> halloumi saganaki</strong>,<strong> salad </strong>and<strong> pitta quarters </strong>to the side</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a crack of<strong> black pepper</strong> to the hummus<strong> </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
